Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,跟神永學姐畫的一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我可以看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以 請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}但是 是一個叫竹谷實可子畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我現在是竹谷實可子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,波戶 你怎麼換回這身打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:49.76,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たいよう　たいよう　あーしたいよう！Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:49.76,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}渴望 渴望 渴望那樣做 {\fnHiragino Maru Gothic Pro W4\fs40}Oh…{/r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:55.06,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たいよう　たいよう　こーしたいよう！Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:55.06,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}渴望 渴望 渴望這樣做 {\fnHiragino Maru Gothic Pro W4\fs40}Oh…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.52,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah げんしけん
